ngineering College, Thrissur, Kerala. Have  research experience of 1 year from NIIST, Trivandrum After the completion of B.Tech in Mechanical Engineering from School Of  Engineering(S.O.E), Cochin University of Science And Technology (CUSAT), I worked in Mumbai at Rabale Industrial Estate, Thane in an Engineering firm named CHROME KRAFT as Mechanical Engineer for 18 months. (Responsible for estimation & planning of Enineering, Procurement & shop fabrication & site installation of Shell Tube Heat Exchangers & Pressure vessels,  Piping & Power Plant Projects.\n\nN.B: Currently I''m in U.A.E on Tourist Visa expiring on 17-Jul-16. Please be free to contact in my UAE no.: 00971505703175. \n \nNote: Certificates and other valid documents will be furnished whenever asked for.\nExpecting an early, positive response.\n  \nKind Regards,\nUmer Illias\nPlanner |  Cost \n \nMob. No: +971-50-570 3175(U.A.E),+91-70 2522 5023(INDIA)', 1466319269, '83.110.98.198', 1),
