(18703, '18/2013', 0, 'Control Specialist (UAE Nationals only)', '', 'Head of Finance', '', 'Finance', '', '', '', 'To support the Head of Finance in their responsibilities of budgeting and long-term planning, management reporting and financial control.', '', '<strong>Budgeting</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n		Annually prepare financial plans/budgets, reflecting the strategic and business objectives defined in the Budget Plan by the Head of Finance.\n		<ul>\n			<li>\n				Prepare and discuss budgets for OPEX and projects together with department heads.</li>\n			<li>\n				Outline changes in staff over coming year together with HR.</li>\n			<li>\n				Consolidate budgets and HR expenses.</li>\n			<li>\n				&nbsp;</li>\n		</ul>\n	</li>\n</ul>', '', '<div data-canvas-width="372.4393030692263" style="left: 111.6px; top: 548.208px; font-size: 18.4px; font-family: sans-serif; transform: scale(0.933705, 1); transform-origin: 0% 0% 0px;">\n	Chartered accountant (or similar qualification) wit</div>\n<div data-canvas-width="326.2587803877636" style="left: 484.199px; top: 548.208px; font-size: 18.4px; font-family: sans-serif; transform: scale(0.919082, 1); transform-origin: 0% 0% 0px;">\n	h proven post qualification experience and</div>\n<div data-canvas-width="285.9341762338252" style="left: 88.9998px; top: 573.807px; font-size: 18.4px; font-family: sans-serif; transform: scale(0.907632, 1); transform-origin: 0% 0% 0px;">\n	minimum experience of five years.</div>\n<div data-canvas-width="8.447804988876651" style="left: 88.9998px; top: 604.269px; font-size: 18.4px; font-family: sans-serif; transform: scale(1.30974, 1); transform-origin: 0% 0% 0px;">\n	&bull;</div>\n<div data-canvas-width="364.64625256407055" style="left: 111.6px; top: 600.607px; font-size: 18.4px; font-family: sans-serif; transform: scale(0.89568, 1); transform-origin: 0% 0% 0px;">\n	Experience of oil and gas operations essential. T</div>\n<div data-canvas-width="308.1352092092491" style="left: 476.4px; top: 600.607px; f